00:12:37,159 --> 00:12:37,519
Look at me.

257
00:12:37,580 --> 00:12:41,460
I'm even blushing to think of it because of the emotion of that.

258
00:12:41,620 --> 00:12:42,360
I was definitely being,

259
00:12:42,720 --> 00:12:43,740
put in my place.

