00:15:46,500 --> 00:15:50,080
the slide pack with the things that I had done well

326
00:15:50,080 --> 00:15:53,779
because I was seeking, you know, the support and investment

327
00:15:53,779 --> 00:15:56,840
of this leader, business leader.

328
00:15:57,379 --> 00:16:00,559
And as I started this slide pack, he interrupted me

329
00:16:00,559 --> 00:16:03,639
and he said, now, have you got slides in there

330
00:16:03,639 --> 00:16:06,960
that tell me your five best failures?

331
00:16:06,960 --> 00:16:10,600
I was completely taken aback.

332
00:16:11,159 --> 00:16:12,759
And I said, no, of course I don't.

333
00:16:12,820 --> 00:16:14,200
I'm here to do the sell job on you.

334
00:16:14,220 --> 00:16:18,360
And he said, well, the sell job for me is for you to tell me

335
00:16:18,360 --> 00:16:21,779
your five best failures and what you learnt from them

336
00:16:21,779 --> 00:16:27,700
because that gives me confidence that you can drive deals

337
00:16:27,700 --> 00:16:30,860
and companies forward and when you're faced with challenges

338
00:16:30,860 --> 00:16:33,919
that you've got good experiences and self-awareness

339
00:16:33,919 --> 00:16:35,480
to be able to deal with them.

340
00:16:36,820 --> 00:16:39,580
Has that resonated with me in the years since?

341
00:16:39,799 --> 00:16:40,080
Yes.

342
00:16:40,559 --> 00:16:41,139
I am.

343
00:16:41,139 --> 00:16:44,779
I absolutely love that and I think more of us should embrace that

344
00:16:44,779 --> 00:16:47,779
because this sense of whether it's tall poppy syndrome

345
00:16:47,779 --> 00:16:52,259
or undermining people because of failures is something

346
00:16:52,259 --> 00:16:56,379
that really holds us back as individuals and as a community

347
00:16:56,379 --> 00:16:59,399
and we need to really push beyond it.

348
00:16:59,679 --> 00:17:02,620
Yeah, and it's unfortunately an Australian thing sometimes,

349
00:17:02,759 --> 00:17:03,019
isn't it?

350
00:17:03,059 --> 00:17:05,779
The tall poppy doesn't resonate when you go to other countries.

