00:18:35,259 --> 00:18:40,539
to support this new venture of mine and I completely underestimated the fact

381
00:18:40,539 --> 00:18:40,619
that I was going to be a lawyer.

382
00:18:40,619 --> 00:18:40,700
I was going to be a lawyer.

