00:18:41,140 --> 00:18:43,819
They knew me as a lawyer but they didn't know me at all

388
00:18:43,819 --> 00:18:47,259
as an entrepreneur or somebody that wanted to start up a new,

389
00:18:47,460 --> 00:18:50,819
I called it adventure capital rather than venture because it was so risky.

