00:18:52,599 --> 00:18:53,440
Yeah, the private equity business.

392
00:18:53,799 --> 00:18:59,619
So I kept getting no's and no's and no's and I had to really go back

393
00:18:59,619 --> 00:19:03,640
and rethink and I had a business partner, Tony, and we agreed.

394
00:19:03,759 --> 00:19:06,640
We had to go about it completely differently and that was

395
00:19:06,640 --> 00:19:10,779
to still identify the opportunity but really highlight the risks.

396
00:19:10,779 --> 00:19:15,279
But also talk about what we'd both done in our lives that we felt

397
00:19:15,279 --> 00:19:21,099
could bring success to this new venture and really de-risk us

398
00:19:21,099 --> 00:19:24,119
as a proposition and it's really something I've taken.

